Package: flagr
Type: Package
Title: Implementation of Flag Aggregation in Eurostat
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: c(person("Mátyás", "Mészáros", email = "matyas.meszaros@ec.europa.eu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Matteo", "Salvati", email = "salvati.matteo@hotmail.fr", role = "aut"))
Description: This package aims at facilitating the aggregations of flags in official statistics 
          according to different methodological guidelines using the R environnement. The package 
          offers 3 options for computing the flags for EU or other aggregates.
